data.title: Watsonville CA funeral home and cremation
data.meta_description: Ave Maria Memorial Chapel staff pride themselves in providing a wide variety of choices including personalized services, cremation memorials and traditional funerals. We feel that serving you is a privilege, and understand that the loss of a loved one is a very personal experience.
